{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896640559,"sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","part":{"id":"prt_d7bb039a9001WYyayXcbAjSblL","messageID":"msg_d7bb025f0001Jvt03SLJ2P2Byy","sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-72a2330aa87b4044aa04057a6714b523","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Design: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 本文档描述了为 agentcube 项目中 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面单元测试的技术实现设计。这些模块构成了系统的核心组件，负责路由、存储和代码执行功能。\n6: \n7: ## 目标\n8: \n9: 1. 为 router、store、picod 模块提供全面的单元测试覆盖\n10: 2. 确保代码质量和可靠性\n11: 3. 提供可维护的测试基础设施\n12: 4. 遵循 Go 测试最佳实践\n13: \n14: ## 架构\n15: \n16: ### 整体架构\n17: \n18: ```\n19: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n20: │                          router                                 │\n21: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n22: │  │   handlers   │  │  middleware  │  │  session_mgr │         │\n23: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n24: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n25: │  │   jwt_mgr    │  │resource_cache│  │ informer_mgr │         │\n26: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n27: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n28:                               │\n29:                               ▼\n30: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n31: │                           store                                 │\n32: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n33: │  │ store_redis  │  │store_valkey  │  │    codec     │         │\n34: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n35: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n36:                               │\n37:                               ▼\n38: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n39: │                          picod                                  │\n40: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n41: │  │   handlers   │  │  middleware  │  │  auth_mgr    │         │\n42: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n43: │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐         │\n44: │  │ workspace_mgr│  │ status_rptr  │  │informr_mgr   │         │\n45: │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘         │\n46: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### 模块职责\n50: \n51: #### Router 模块\n52: - **handlers.go**: HTTP 请求处理逻辑\n53: - **middleware.go**: 中间件（认证、限流、日志、监控）\n54: - **session_manager.go**: 会话管理和沙盒生命周期\n55: - **jwt.go**: JWT 令牌生成和验证\n56: - **resource_cache.go**: Kubernetes 资源缓存\n57: - **informer_manager.go**: Kubernetes informer 管理\n58: - **server.go**: HTTP 服务器启动和配置\n59: \n60: #### Store 模块\n61: - **store.go**: 存储接口定义\n62: - **store_redis.go**: Redis 存储实现\n63: - **store_valkey.go**: ValKey 存储实现\n64: - **codec.go**: 数据序列化/反序列化\n65: - **singleton.go**: 存储实例管理\n66: \n67: #### Picod 模块\n68: - **handlers.go**: 文件操作和命令执行处理\n69: - **middleware.go**: 认证中间件\n70: - **auth.go**: 认证管理器\n71: - **workspace_manager.go**: 工作空间管理\n72: - **status_reporter.go**: 状态报告\n73: - **informer.go**: Kubernetes informer 集成\n74: - **server.go**: HTTP 服务器\n75: \n76: ## 数据结构\n77: \n78: ### Router 模块数据结构\n79: \n80: #### 核心类型\n81: \n82: ```go\n83: // Server 主服务器结构\n84: type Server struct {\n85:     config         *Config\n86:     engine         *gin.Engine\n87:     httpServer     *http.Server\n88:     sessionManager SessionManager\n89:     storeClient    store.Store\n90:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n91:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n92:     handler        *Handler\n93:     limiter        *ConcurrencyLimiter\n94:     metrics        *Metrics\n95:     mu             sync.RWMutex\n96: }\n97: \n98: // Handler HTTP 处理器\n99: type Handler struct {\n100:     sessionManager SessionManager\n101:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n102:     reverseProxy   *ReverseProxy\n103: }\n104: \n105: // SessionManager 会话管理器接口\n106: type SessionManager interface {\n107:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n108:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n109:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n110:     InitializeInformers(clientset kubernetes.Interface, namespace string, resyncPeriod time.Duration) error\n111:     StartInformers()\n112:     StopInformers()\n113:     WaitForCacheSync(ctx context.Context) bool\n114: }\n115: \n116: // ResourceCache 资源缓存\n117: type ResourceCache struct {\n118:     mu               sync.RWMutex\n119:     agentRuntimes    map[string]*agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime\n120:     codeInterpreters map[string]*agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter\n121:     resourceVersions map[string]string\n122: }\n123: ```\n124: \n125: #### 错误类型\n126: \n127: ```go\n128: // HTTPError HTTP 错误接口\n129: type HTTPError interface {\n130:     Error() string\n131:     HTTPStatusCode() int\n132:     ErrorCode() string\n133: }\n134: \n135: // SandboxNotFoundError 沙盒未找到错误\n136: type SandboxNotFoundError struct {\n137:     SessionID string\n138:     Name      string\n139:     Namespace string\n140:     Kind      string\n141: }\n142: \n143: // ValidationError 验证错误\n144: type ValidationError struct {\n145:     Field   string\n146:     Message string\n147: }\n148: \n149: // WorkloadManagerError 工作负载管理器错误\n150: type WorkloadManagerError struct {\n151:     Message string\n152:     Code    int\n153: }\n154: ```\n155: \n156: ### Store 模块数据结构\n157: \n158: ```go\n159: // Store 存储接口\n160: type Store interface {\n161:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n162:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n163:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n164:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n165:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n166:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n167:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n168:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n169:     Close() error\n170: }\n171: \n172: // redisStore Redis 存储实现\n173: type redisStore struct {\n174:     cli                  *redis.Client\n175:     sessionPrefix        string\n176:     expiryIndexKey       string\n177:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n178: }\n179: ```\n180: \n181: ### Picod 模块数据结构\n182: \n183: ```go\n184: // Server PicoD 服务器\n185: type Server struct {\n186:     engine           *gin.Engine\n187:     config           Config\n188:     authManager      *AuthManager\n189:     startTime        time.Time\n190:     workspaceDir     string\n191:     httpServer       *http.Server\n192:     k8sClient        *K8sClient\n193:     workspaceManager *WorkspaceManager\n194:     statusReporter   *StatusReporter\n195:     informerManager  *InformerManager\n196: }\n197: \n198: // ExecuteRequest 执行请求\n199: type ExecuteRequest struct {\n200:     Command     []string            `json:\"command\"`\n201:     WorkingDir  string              `json:\"workingDir\"`\n202:     Env         map[string]string   `json:\"env\"`\n203:     Timeout     string              `json:\"timeout\"`\n204: }\n205: \n206: // ExecuteResponse 执行响应\n207: type ExecuteResponse struct {\n208:     Stdout    string      `json:\"stdout\"`\n209:     Stderr    string      `json:\"stderr\"`\n210:     ExitCode  int         `json:\"exitCode\"`\n211:     Duration  float64     `json:\"duration\"`\n212:     StartTime time.Time   `json:\"startTime\"`\n213:     EndTime   time.Time   `json:\"endTime\"`\n214: }\n215: ```\n216: \n217: ## API 契约\n218: \n219: ### Router 模块 API\n220: \n221: #### HTTP 端点\n222: \n223: ```\n224: # 健康检查\n225: GET /health/live\n226: GET /health/ready\n227: \n228: # 会话管理\n229: POST /v1/sessions/namespaces/:namespace/:kind/:name\n230: GET  /v1/sessions/:sessionID\n231: \n232: # 资源调用\n233: ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path\n234: ANY /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path\n235: ```\n236: \n237: #### 内部接口\n238: \n239: ```go\n240: // SessionManager 接口方法签名\n241: GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n242: CreateSession(ctx context.Context, name string, namespace string, kind string) (string, *types.SandboxInfo, error)\n243: ListSessions(ctx context.Context) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n244: \n245: // JWTManager 接口方法签名\n246: GenerateToken(sessionID string) (string, error)\n247: ValidateToken(token string) (*JWTClaims, error)\n248: ```\n249: \n250: ### Store 模块 API\n251: \n252: ```go\n253: // Store 接口方法签名\n254: Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n255: GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n256: StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n257: UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n258: DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n259: ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n260: ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n261: UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n262: Close() error\n263: ```\n264: \n265: ### Picod 模块 API\n266: \n267: #### HTTP 端点\n268: \n269: ```\n270: # 健康检查\n271: GET /health\n272: \n273: # 认证保护的端点\n274: POST /api/execute\n275: POST /api/files\n276: GET  /api/files\n277: GET  /api/files/*path\n278: ```\n279: \n280: #### 请求/响应类型\n281: \n282: ```go\n283: // ExecuteRequest 命令执行请求\n284: type ExecuteRequest struct {\n285:     Command     []string          `json:\"command\"`\n286:     WorkingDir  string            `json:\"workingDir\"`\n287:     Env         map[string]string `json:\"env\"`\n288:     Timeout     string            `json:\"timeout\"`\n289: }\n290: \n291: // ExecuteResponse 命令执行响应\n292: type ExecuteResponse struct {\n293:     Stdout    string    `json:\"stdout\"`\n294:     Stderr    string    `json:\"stderr\"`\n295:     ExitCode  int       `json:\"exitCode\"`\n296:     Duration  float64   `json:\"duration\"`\n297:     StartTime time.Time `json:\"startTime\"`\n298:     EndTime   time.Time `json:\"endTime\"`\n299: }\n300: \n301: // FileEntry 文件条目\n302: type FileEntry struct {\n303:     Name     string      `json:\"name\"`\n304:     Size     int64       `json:\"size\"`\n305:     Modified time.Time   `json:\"modified\"`\n306:     Mode     string      `json:\"mode\"`\n307:     IsDir    bool        `json:\"isDir\"`\n308: }\n309: ```\n310: \n311: ## 错误处理\n312: \n313: ### 错误层次结构\n314: \n315: ```\n316: HTTPError (interface)\n317: ├── SandboxNotFoundError\n318: ├── SessionExpiredError\n319: ├── WorkloadManagerError\n320: └── ValidationError\n321: ```\n322: \n323: ### 错误处理策略\n324: \n325: #### Router 模块错误处理\n326: \n327: 1. **验证错误**: 返回 400 状态码和详细错误信息\n328: 2. **未找到错误**: 返回 404 状态码\n329: 3. **认证错误**: 返回 401 状态码\n330: 4. **服务器错误**: 返回 500 状态码并记录日志\n331: \n332: #### Store 模块错误处理\n333: \n334: 1. **连接错误**: 返回 wrapped 错误，包含原始错误\n335: 2. **未找到错误**: 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n336: 3. **序列化错误**: 返回 wrapped 错误\n337: 4. **验证错误**: 参数校验失败时返回描述性错误\n338: \n339: #### Picod 模块错误处理\n340: \n341: 1. **命令执行错误**: 捕获并返回退出码\n342: 2. **文件操作错误**: 返回适当的 HTTP 状态码\n343: 3. **认证错误**: 返回 401 状态码\n344: 4. **超时错误**: 返回特殊的超时退出码\n345: \n346: ### 错误码定义\n347: \n348: ```go\n349: // Router 错误码\n350: const (\n351:     ErrSandboxNotFound        = \"SANDBOX_NOT_FOUND\"\n352:     ErrSessionExpired         = \"SESSION_EXPIRED\"\n353:     ErrWorkloadManagerError   = \"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_ERROR\"\n354:     ErrValidationError        = \"VALIDATION_ERROR\"\n355:     ErrJWTSigningFailed       = \"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\"\n356:     ErrSandboxUnreachable     = \"SANDBOX_UNREACHABLE\"\n357:     ErrServerOverloaded       = \"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"\n358:     ErrSessionManagerNotReady = \"SESSION_MANAGER_NOT_READY\"\n359: )\n360: \n361: // Store 错误码\n362: var ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n363: \n364: // Picod 错误码\n365: const (\n366:     ErrInvalidCommand    = \"INVALID_COMMAND\"\n367:     ErrEmptyCommand      = \"EMPTY_COMMAND\"\n368:     ErrInvalidTimeout    = \"INVALID_TIMEOUT\"\n369:     ErrMissingAuthHeader = \"MISSING_AUTH_HEADER\"\n370:     ErrFileNotFound      = \"FILE_NOT_FOUND\"\n371:     ErrDirectoryNotFound = \"DIRECTORY_NOT_FOUND\"\n372:     ErrPathIsDirectory   = \"PATH_IS_DIRECTORY\"\n373:     ErrServerInternal    = \"SERVER_INTERNAL\"\n374: )\n375: ```\n376: \n377: ## 测试策略\n378: \n379: ### 测试组织结构\n380: \n381: ```\n382: pkg/\n383: ├── router/\n384: │   ├── handlers_test.go\n385: │   ├── middleware_test.go\n386: │   ├── session_manager_test.go\n387: │   ├── jwt_test.go\n388: │   ├── resource_cache_test.go\n389: │   ├── informer_manager_test.go\n390: │   ├── config_test.go\n391: │   └── server_test.go\n392: ├── store/\n393: │   ├── store_test.go\n394: │   ├── store_redis_test.go\n395: │   ├── store_valkey_test.go\n396: │   ├── codec_test.go\n397: │   └── singleton_test.go\n398: └── picod/\n399:     ├── handlers_test.go\n400:     ├── middleware_test.go\n401:     ├── auth_test.go\n402:     ├── workspace_manager_test.go\n403:     ├── status_reporter_test.go\n404:     ├── informer_test.go\n405:     └── server_test.go\n406: ```\n407: \n408: ### 测试框架和工具\n409: \n410: #### 主要测试框架\n411: - **标准库 `testing`**: Go 标准测试框架\n412: - **testify/assert**: 断言库，提供更丰富的断言方法\n413: - **testify/require**: 必要断言，失败时立即停止测试\n414: \n415: #### Mock 和 Stub 工具\n416: - **httptest**: HTTP 测试服务器\n417: - **fake kubernetes clientset**: Kubernetes 客户端模拟\n418: - **miniredis**: Redis 内存数据库模拟\n419: - **自定义 fake 实现**: 用于自定义接口的模拟\n420: \n421: #### 辅助工具\n422: - **gonic/gin.TestMode**: Gin 框架测试模式\n423: - **google/uuid**: UUID 生成和验证\n424: - **testify/mock**: Mock 接口实现\n425: \n426: ### 测试覆盖率目标\n427: \n428: | 模块     | 目标覆盖率 | 优先级 |\n429: |---------|-----------|--------|\n430: | router  | ≥80%      | 高     |\n431: | store   | ≥85%      | 高     |\n432: | picod   | ≥75%      | 中     |\n433: \n434: ### 测试分类\n435: \n436: #### 单元测试\n437: \n438: **目标**: 测试单个函数或方法的行为\n439: \n440: **特点**:\n441: - 快速执行（毫秒级）\n442: - 无外部依赖\n443: - 可重复运行\n444: - 覆盖所有代码路径\n445: \n446: **示例**:\n447: ```go\n448: func TestNewHandler(t *testing.T) {\n449:     jwtManager, err := NewJWTManager(fake.NewSimpleClientset(), \"test\")\n450:     require.NoError(t, err)\n451: \n452:     handler := NewHandler(nil, jwtManager, nil)\n453:     assert.NotNil(t, handler)\n454:     assert.NotNil(t, handler.jwtManager)\n455: }\n456: ```\n457: \n458: #### 集成测试\n459: \n460: **目标**: 测试多个组件之间的交互\n461: \n462: **特点**:\n463: - 使用真实依赖的模拟版本\n464: - 测试组件间的数据流\n465: - 验证接口契约\n466: \n467: **示例**:\n468: ```go\n469: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession(t *testing.T) {\n470:     server := httptest.NewServer(http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n471:         // Mock workload manager response\n472:     }))\n473:     defer server.Close()\n474: \n475:     fakeStore := &fakeStore{}\n476:     manager, err := NewSessionManager(fakeStore, server.URL)\n477:     require.NoError(t, err)\n478: \n479:     sessionID, sandboxInfo, err := manager.CreateSession(context.Background(), \"test\", \"default\", types.AgentRuntimeKind)\n480:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n481:     assert.NotEmpty(t, sessionID)\n482:     assert.NotNil(t, sandboxInfo)\n483: }\n484: ```\n485: \n486: #### 表驱动测试\n487: \n488: **目标**: 测试函数在不同输入下的行为\n489: \n490: **特点**:\n491: - 清晰的测试用例组织\n492: - 易于添加新的测试场景\n493: - 一致的断言逻辑\n494: \n495: **示例**:\n496: ```go\n497: func TestHandleHealthReady(t *testing.T) {\n498:     tests := []struct {\n499:         name           string\n500:         sessionManager SessionManager\n501:         jwtManager     *JWTManager\n502:         expectedStatus int\n503:     }{\n504:         {\n505:             name:           \"session manager not ready\",\n506:             sessionManager: nil,\n507:             jwtManager:     func() *JWTManager { mgr, _ := NewJWTManager(fake.NewSimpleClientset(), \"test\"); return mgr }(),\n508:             expectedStatus: http.StatusServiceUnavailable,\n509:         },\n510:         {\n511:             name:           \"JWT manager not ready\",\n512:             sessionManager: nil,\n513:             jwtManager:     nil,\n514:             expectedStatus: http.StatusServiceUnavailable,\n515:         },\n516:     }\n517: \n518:     for _, tt := range tests {\n519:         t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {\n520:             handler := NewHandler(tt.sessionManager, tt.jwtManager, nil)\n521:             // ... test implementation\n522:         })\n523:     }\n524: }\n525: ```\n526: \n527: ### Mock 策略\n528: \n529: #### 接口 Mock\n530: \n531: ```go\n532: // Fake Store 实现\n533: type fakeStore struct {\n534:     sandboxes map[string]*types.SandboxInfo\n535: }\n536: \n537: func (fs *fakeStore) GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error) {\n538:     if fs.sandboxes == nil {\n539:         return nil, store.ErrNotFound\n540:     }\n541:     sandbox, exists := fs.sandboxes[sessionID]\n542:     if !exists {\n543:         return nil, store.ErrNotFound\n544:     }\n545:     return sandbox, nil\n546: }\n547: ```\n548: \n549: #### HTTP Mock\n550: \n551: ```go\n552: func TestSessionManager_CreateSession(t *testing.T) {\n553:     server := httptest.NewServer(http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n554:         if r.Method == http.MethodPost && r.URL.Path == \"/v1/agent-runtime\" {\n555:             w.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n556:             w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n557:             w.Write([]byte(`{\n558:                 \"sessionId\": \"test-session-id\",\n559:                 \"sandboxId\": \"test-sandbox-id\",\n560:                 \"sandboxName\": \"test-sandbox\",\n561:                 \"entryPoints\": []\n562:             }`))\n563:         }\n564:     }))\n565:     defer server.Close()\n566: \n567:     // ... test implementation\n568: }\n569: ```\n570: \n571: ### 测试辅助函数\n572: \n573: #### 设置和清理\n574: \n575: ```go\n576: func setupTestServer(t *testing.T) *Server {\n577:     workspace := t.TempDir()\n578:     _, publicKey := generateTestKeyPair(t)\n579:     publicKeyPEM := publicKeyToPEM(t, publicKey)\n580: \n581:     os.Setenv(PublicKeyEnvVar, publicKeyPEM)\n582:     defer os.Unsetenv(PublicKeyEnvVar)\n583: \n584:     config := Config{\n585:         Port:      0,\n586:         Workspace: workspace,\n587:     }\n588: \n589:     server, err := NewServer(config)\n590:     require.NoError(t, err)\n591:     gin.SetMode(gin.TestMode)\n592: \n593:     return server\n594: }\n595: ```\n596: \n597: #### 数据生成\n598: \n599: ```go\n600: func generateTestSandboxInfo() *types.SandboxInfo {\n601:     return &types.SandboxInfo{\n602:         SessionID:    \"test-session-\" + uuid.New().String(),\n603:         SandboxName:  \"test-sandbox\",\n604:         WorkloadName: \"test-workload\",\n605:         Namespace:    \"default\",\n606:         Kind:         \"AgentRuntime\",\n607:         Status:       \"running\",\n608:         CreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n609:         ExpiresAt:    time.Now().Add(8 * time.Hour),\n610:         PodIP:        \"10.0.0.1\",\n611:     }\n612: }\n613: ```\n614: \n615: ### 测试场景\n616: \n617: #### Router 模块测试场景\n618: \n619: **handlers_test.go**\n620: - ✓ Handler 初始化\n621: - ✓ 健康检查端点 (live/ready)\n622: - ✓ 会话 ID 提取\n623: - ✓ 会话创建验证\n624: - ✓ 资源调用验证\n625: - ✓ 错误响应格式\n626: \n627: **middleware_test.go**\n628: - ✓ 并发限制中间件\n629: - ✓ 日志中间件\n630: - ✓ 恢复中间件\n631: - ✓ 关联 ID 中间件\n632: - ✓ JWT 认证中间件\n633: - ✓ 指标中间件\n634: \n635: **session_manager_test.go**\n636: - ✓ 会话管理器初始化\n637: - ✓ Informer 初始化和启动\n638: - ✓ 会话创建（成功/失败）\n639: - ✓ 沙盒获取（缓存命中/未命中）\n640: - ✓ 会话列表\n641: - ✓ 资源状态检查\n642: - ✓ 资源删除检测\n643: \n644: **jwt_test.go**\n645: - ✓ JWT 令牌生成\n646: - ✓ JWT 令牌验证\n647: - ✓ 过期令牌处理\n648: - ✓ 无效令牌处理\n649: \n650: **resource_cache_test.go**\n651: - ✓ 资源缓存更新\n652: - ✓ 资源缓存查询\n653: - ✓ 资源缓存删除\n654: - ✓ 资源版本检查\n655: - ✓ 并发安全性\n656: \n657: **informer_manager_test.go**\n658: - ✓ Informer 管理器初始化\n659: - ✓ Informer 启动和停止\n660: - ✓ 缓存同步等待\n661: - ✓ 空客户端集处理\n662: \n663: **config_test.go**\n664: - ✓ 配置验证\n665: - ✓ 默认配置\n666: - ✓ TLS 配置\n667: - ✓ 超时配置\n668: \n669: **server_test.go**\n670: - ✓ 服务器初始化\n671: - ✓ 服务器启动和关闭\n672: - ✓ 中间件应用\n673: - ✓ 路由设置\n674: - ✓ 指标收集\n675: \n676: #### Store 模块测试场景\n677: \n678: **store_test.go**\n679: - ✓ 存储连接测试\n680: - ✓ 沙盒存储和获取\n681: - ✓ 沙盒更新\n682: - ✓ 沙盒删除\n683: - ✓ 会话活动更新\n684: - ✓ 过期沙盒列表\n685: - ✓ 非活跃沙盒列表\n686: - ✓ 错误处理\n687: \n688: **store_redis_test.go**\n689: - ✓ Redis 连接\n690: - ✓ Redis 特定操作\n691: - ✓ 管道操作\n692: - ✓ 索引管理\n693: \n694: **store_valkey_test.go**\n695: - ✓ ValKey 连接\n696: - ✓ ValKey 特定操作\n697: - ✓ 与 Redis 实现兼容性\n698: \n699: **codec_test.go**\n700: - ✓ 沙盒信息序列化\n701: - ✓ 沙盒信息反序列化\n702: - ✓ 错误处理\n703: \n704: **singleton_test.go**\n705: - ✓ 单例模式\n706: - ✓ 不同存储类型初始化\n707: - ✓ 配置验证\n708: \n709: #### Picod 模块测试场景\n710: \n711: **handlers_test.go**\n712: - ✓ 命令执行处理器\n713: - ✓ 文件上传处理器（multipart）\n714: - ✓ 文件上传处理器（base64）\n715: - ✓ 文件列表处理器\n716: - ✓ 文件下载处理器\n717: - ✓ 健康检查处理器\n718: - ✓ 路径清理\n719: - ✓ 文件模式解析\n720: \n721: **middleware_test.go**\n722: - ✓ 认证中间件\n723: - ✓ 有效令牌处理\n724: - ✓ 无效令牌处理\n725: - ✓ 缺失认证头处理\n726: \n727: **auth_test.go**\n728: - ✓ 认证管理器初始化\n729: - ✓ 令牌生成和验证\n730: - ✓ 密钥对生成\n731: - ✓ 错误处理\n732: \n733: **workspace_manager_test.go**\n734: - ✓ 工作空间初始化\n735: - ✓ 文件操作\n736: - ✓ 目录管理\n737: - ✓ 权限处理\n738: \n739: **status_reporter_test.go**\n740: - ✓ 状态报告器初始化\n741: - ✓ 状态更新\n742: - ✓ 周期性报告\n743: \n744: **informer_test.go**\n745: - ✓ Informer 设置\n746: - ✓ 事件处理\n747: - ✓ 缓存同步\n748: \n749: **server_test.go**\n750: - ✓ 服务器初始化\n751: - ✓ 服务器启动和关闭\n752: - ✓ 路由注册\n753: - ✓ 中间件应用\n754: \n755: ### 测试执行\n756: \n757: #### 本地测试运行\n758: \n759: ```bash\n760: # 运行所有测试\n761: go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... ./pkg/picod/...\n762: \n763: # 运行特定包测试\n764: go test ./pkg/router/\n765: \n766: # 运行特定测试\n767: go test ./pkg/router/ -run TestNewHandler\n768: \n769: # 运行测试并显示覆盖率\n770: go test -cover ./pkg/router/...\n771: \n772: # 生成覆盖率报告\n773: go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/...\n774: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n775: \n776: # 运行基准测试\n777: go test -bench=. ./pkg/...\n778: \n779: # 运行竞态检测\n780: go test -race ./pkg/...\n781: ```\n782: \n783: #### CI/CD 集成\n784: \n785: ```yaml\n786: # .github/workflows/test.yml 示例\n787: name: Tests\n788: \n789: on: [push, pull_request]\n790: \n791: jobs:\n792:   test:\n793:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n794:     steps:\n795:       - uses: actions/checkout@v3\n796:       - uses: actions/setup-go@v4\n797:         with:\n798:           go-version: '1.21'\n799:       - name: Run tests\n800:         run: |\n801:           go test -race -coverprofile=coverage.out -covermode=atomic ./pkg/...\n802:       - name: Upload coverage\n803:         uses: codecov/codecov-action@v3\n804:         with:\n805:           files: ./coverage.out\n806: ```\n807: \n808: ### 测试最佳实践\n809: \n810: 1. **测试命名**: 使用描述性的测试名称，格式为 `Test<FunctionName>_<Scenario>`\n811: \n812: 2. **表驱动测试**: 对于有多个测试场景的函数，使用表驱动测试\n813: \n814: 3. **子测试**: 使用 `t.Run()` 组织相关测试\n815: \n816: 4. **断言**: 使用 `assert` 进行一般断言，`require` 进行关键断言\n817: \n818: 5. **清理**: 使用 `defer` 或 `t.Cleanup()` 进行资源清理\n819: \n820: 6. **隔离**: 每个测试应该是独立的，不依赖于其他测试\n821: \n822: 7. **并发安全**: 测试并发代码时使用 `-race` 标志\n823: \n824: 8. **Mock 依赖**: 使用 fake 实现替代真实依赖\n825: \n826: 9. **错误测试**: 测试错误路径，不仅仅是成功路径\n827: \n828: 10. **边界条件**: 测试边界条件和特殊情况\n829: \n830: ## 实施计划\n831: \n832: ### 阶段 1: Router 模块测试（优先级：高）\n833: \n834: 1. 完善 `handlers_test.go`\n835: 2. 完善 `middleware_test.go`\n836: 3. 完善 `session_manager_test.go`\n837: 4. 完善 `jwt_test.go`\n838: 5. 新增 `resource_cache_test.go`\n839: 6. 新增 `informer_manager_test.go`\n840: 7. 完善 `config_test.go`\n841: 8. 新增 `server_test.go`\n842: \n843: ### 阶段 2: Store 模块测试（优先级：高）\n844: \n845: 1. 完善 `store_test.go`\n846: 2. 新增 `store_redis_test.go`\n847: 3. 新增 `store_valkey_test.go`\n848: 4. 新增 `codec_test.go`\n849: 5. 新增 `singleton_test.go`\n850: \n851: ### 阶段 3: Picod 模块测试（优先级：中）\n852: \n853: 1. 完善 `handlers_test.go`\n854: 2. 完善 `middleware_test.go`\n855: 3. 完善 `auth_test.go`\n856: 4. 新增 `workspace_manager_test.go`\n857: 5. 新增 `status_reporter_test.go`\n858: 6. 新增 `informer_test.go`\n859: 7. 完善 `server_test.go`\n860: \n861: ### 验收标准\n862: \n863: - 所有新测试通过\n864: - 代码覆盖率达标\n865: - 无竞态条件警告\n866: - 测试执行时间合理\n867: - CI/CD 流水线集成成功\n868: \n869: ## 依赖关系\n870: \n871: ### 测试依赖\n872: \n873: ```go\n874: // go.mod 中的测试依赖\n875: require (\n876:     github.com/stretchr/testify v1.8.4  // 测试框架\n877:     github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.32.0  // Redis 模拟\n878:     k8s.io/client-go v0.28.0  // Kubernetes 客户端（包含 fake 实现）\n879: )\n880: ```\n881: \n882: ### 运行时依赖\n883: \n884: ```go\n885: // 主要运行时依赖\n886: require (\n887:     github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.9.1  // Web 框架\n888:     github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.0.0  // JWT 处理\n889:     github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.0.5  // Redis 客户端\n890:     k8s.io/api v0.28.0  // Kubernetes API\n891:     k8s.io/apimachinery v0.28.0  // Kubernetes API machinery\n892:     k8s.io/client-go v0.28.0  // Kubernetes 客户端\n893: )\n894: ```\n895: \n896: ## 性能考虑\n897: \n898: ### 测试性能优化\n899: \n900: 1. **并行测试**: 使用 `t.Parallel()` 运行独立测试\n901: 2. **缓存重用**: 在包级别初始化共享资源\n902: 3. **选择性运行**: 使用 `-run` 标志运行特定测试\n903: 4. **超时控制**: 为长时间运行的测试设置超时\n904: \n905: ### 基准测试\n906: \n907: ```go\n908: func BenchmarkResourceCache_GetAgentRuntime(b *testing.B) {\n909:     cache := NewResourceCache()\n910:     ar := &agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n911:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n912:             Name:      \"test\",\n913:             Namespace: \"default\",\n914:         },\n915:     }\n916:     cache.UpdateAgentRuntime(ar)\n917: \n918:     b.ResetTimer()\n919:     for i := 0; i < b.N; i++ {\n920:         cache.GetAgentRuntime(\"default\", \"test\")\n921:     }\n922: }\n923: ```\n924: \n925: ## 文档\n926: \n927: ### 测试文档\n928: \n929: 每个测试文件应包含：\n930: - 包级别的文档注释\n931: - 复杂测试函数的文档注释\n932: - 测试辅助函数的文档注释\n933: \n934: ### 示例\n935: \n936: ```go\n937: // Package router_test provides unit tests for the router package.\n938: //\n939: // These tests cover the HTTP handlers, middleware, session management,\n940: // JWT authentication, resource caching, and informer management.\n941: package router_test\n942: \n943: // TestNewHandler verifies that a new Handler instance is created correctly.\n944: // It ensures that the handler is properly initialized with the provided\n945: // JWT manager and that the handler is not nil.\n946: func TestNewHandler(t *testing.T) {\n947:     // ... implementation\n948: }\n949: ```\n950: \n951: ## 维护和更新\n952: \n953: ### 测试维护指南\n954: \n955: 1. **代码变更时更新测试**: 修改代码时同步更新相关测试\n956: 2. **定期审查覆盖率**: 定期检查测试覆盖率报告\n957: 3. **重构测试**: 随着代码演进重构测试以提高可维护性\n958: 4. **删除过时测试**: 移除不再相关的测试用例\n959: 5. **添加新测试**: 为新功能添加相应的测试\n960: \n961: ### 持续改进\n962: \n963: 1. **监控测试执行时间**: 识别并优化慢速测试\n964: 2. **分析失败测试**: 建立测试失败分析流程\n965: 3. **分享测试最佳实践**: 在团队中推广测试最佳实践\n966: 4. **自动化测试更新**: 尽可能自动化测试维护任务\n967: \n968: ## 总结\n969: \n970: 本设计文档为 AR-039 Go 单元测试提供了全面的技术实施指南。通过遵循本文档中描述的架构、数据结构、API 契约、错误处理和测试策略，可以为 router、store 和 picod 模块构建高质量、可维护的单元测试套件。\n971: \n972: 实施此设计将带来以下好处：\n973: - 提高代码质量和可靠性\n974: - 加速开发和调试过程\n975: - 降低回归风险\n976: - 提供代码行为的文档\n977: - 支持安全的重构和演进\n978: \n979: 通过阶段化的实施计划和明确的验收标准，可以确保测试工作的有序进行和成功交付。\n\n(End of file - total 979 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Design: AR-039 — Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档描述了为 agentcube 项目中 `pkg/router`、`pkg/store` 和 `pkg/picod` 模块编写全面单元测试的技术实现设计。这些模块构成了系统的核心组件，负责路由、存储和代码执行功能。\n\n## 目标\n\n1. 为 router、store、picod 模块提供全面的单元测试覆盖\n2. 确保代码质量和可靠性\n3. 提供可维护的测试基础设施\n4. 遵循 Go 测试最佳实践\n\n## 架构\n\n### 整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                          router                                 │","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775896640530,"end":1775896640556}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896640561,"sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","part":{"id":"prt_d7bb03bf40018VOL5eXpWq8eqE","messageID":"msg_d7bb025f0001Jvt03SLJ2P2Byy","sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-050c99e834464ae4b812eb80b6f77b7e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/test_spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/test_spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n2: \n3: 要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n4: \n5: ## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n6: - **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n7: - **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n8: - **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n9: \n10: ## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n11: - **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n12: - **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n13: - **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n14: \n15: ## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n16: - **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n17: - **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n18: \n19: ## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n20: - **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。\n21: - **TestCase-PD-002**: 错误处理。发送语法错误代码，预期 stderr 包含 `SyntaxError`。\n22: \n23: ## 5. Python SDK 测试\n24: - **TestCase-SDK-001**: 上下文管理器验证。使用 `with CodeInterpreterClient(...) as client:` 确保结束时自动调用 `close()`。\n25: - **TestCase-SDK-002**: 异常映射。服务端返回 500 时，SDK 抛出自定义 `AgentCubeError` 而非原始 HTTP 错误。\n26: \n27: ## 实施要求\n28: - **Go 代码**：必须位于对应的 `*_test.go` 中，可通过 `go test ./...` 运行。\n29: - **Python 代码**：必须位于 `tests/` 目录或 `test_*.py` 文件中，可通过 `pytest` 运行。\n\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n\n要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n\n## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n- **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n\n## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n- **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n- **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n- **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n\n## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n- **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n- **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n\n## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n- **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/test_spec.md","time":{"start":1775896640532,"end":1775896640560}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775896640569,"sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","part":{"id":"prt_d7bb0375e001hI02tvIaqUPN4l","messageID":"msg_d7bb025f0001Jvt03SLJ2P2Byy","sessionID":"ses_284500342ffe3Yogb7xdZXscIa","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-c312726f477e4538bfca77a5ef23c544","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/test/e2e/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/test/e2e/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-041: E2E Integration Tests — Task Checklist\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: This task checklist breaks down the implementation of E2E integration tests for the AgentCube project into atomic, independently verifiable tasks.\n6: \n7: **Module:** `test/e2e`  \n8: **Language:** Go  \n9: **Size:** L  \n10: **Status:** Ready for Implementation\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Phase 1: Foundation (Framework Infrastructure)\n15: \n16: ### 1.1 Create Test Framework Structure\n17: \n18: **Task ID:** T-1.1  \n19: **Description:** Create directory structure and package initialization for E2E test framework\n20: \n21: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n22: - Directory `test/e2e/framework/` exists\n23: - Directory `test/e2e/agentruntime/` exists\n24: - Directory `test/e2e/codeinterpreter/` exists\n25: - Directory `test/e2e/integration/` exists\n26: - Directory `test/e2e/manifests/` exists\n27: - Directory `test/e2e/manifests/agentruntimes/` exists\n28: - Directory `test/e2e/manifests/codeinterpreters/` exists\n29: - Directory `test/e2e/manifests/deployments/` exists\n30: - All directories contain `go.mod` package declaration `package e2e` or `package framework`\n31: - `go build ./test/e2e/...` succeeds without errors\n32: \n33: **Dependencies:** None  \n34: **Estimated Time:** 30 minutes\n35: \n36: ---\n37: \n38: ### 1.2 Implement TestFramework Core\n39: \n40: **Task ID:** T-1.2  \n41: **Description:** Implement core TestFramework struct with Kubernetes client initialization\n42: \n43: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/framework.go`\n44: \n45: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n46: - `TestFramework` struct exists with fields: config, clientset, agentClient, namespace, clusterName, httpClient, cleanup\n47: - `FrameworkOptions` struct exists with configurable options\n48: - `NewDefaultFramework(name string) *TestFramework` function works and returns framework with defaults\n49: - `NewFramework(name string, opts FrameworkOptions) *TestFramework` function works and accepts custom options\n50: - Default namespace format is `e2e-test-<random>` when not specified\n51: - Default timeout is 5 minutes when not specified\n52: - Default poll interval is 1 second when not specified\n53: - `go test -c ./test/e2e/framework/` compiles successfully\n54: - Unit tests verify framework initialization with various options\n55: \n56: **Dependencies:** T-1.1  \n57: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ### 1.3 Implement Kubernetes Environment Setup\n62: \n63: **Task ID:** T-1.3  \n64: **Description:** Add Kubernetes environment setup and teardown methods to TestFramework\n65: \n66: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/framework.go` (extend)\n67: \n68: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n69: - `AgentCubeReady() bool` method checks if AgentCube deployment is ready\n70: - `Setup() error` method creates test namespace if needed\n71: - `Cleanup() error` method deletes test namespace and registered cleanup functions\n72: - `Namespace() string` method returns current test namespace\n73: - `Clientset() *kubernetes.Clientset` method returns Kubernetes client\n74: - `AgentClient() *agentclient.Clientset` method returns AgentCube client\n75: - Cleanup functions are executed in reverse order\n76: - Setup creates namespace with random suffix if not specified\n77: - Cleanup respects `SkipCleanup` option\n78: - Unit tests verify setup/teardown behavior\n79: \n80: **Dependencies:** T-1.2  \n81: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ### 1.4 Implement AgentRuntimeHelper\n86: \n87: **Task ID:** T-1.4  \n88: **Description:** Implement helper utilities for AgentRuntime CRUD operations\n89: \n90: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/helpers.go`\n91: \n92: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n93: - `AgentRuntimeHelper` struct exists with framework reference\n94: - `NewAgentRuntimeHelper(f *TestFramework) *AgentRuntimeHelper` constructor works\n95: - `CreateAgentRuntime(ctx, agent) (*AgentRuntime, error)` creates AgentRuntime resource\n96: - `GetAgentRuntime(ctx, name) (*AgentRuntime, error)` retrieves AgentRuntime by name\n97: - `WaitForAgentRuntimeReady(ctx, name, timeout) error` waits until AgentRuntime is ready\n98: - `CreateSession(ctx, req) (*CreateSandboxResponse, error)` creates session via workload-manager\n99: - `InvokeSession(ctx, sessionID, payload, headers) (*InvokeResponse, error)` invokes session\n100: - `DeleteSession(ctx, sessionID) error` deletes session\n101: - All methods handle context cancellation properly\n102: - Unit tests verify each helper method\n103: \n104: **Dependencies:** T-1.3  \n105: **Estimated Time:** 3 hours\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ### 1.5 Implement CodeInterpreterHelper\n110: \n111: **Task ID:** T-1.5  \n112: **Description:** Implement helper utilities for CodeInterpreter operations\n113: \n114: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/helpers.go` (extend)\n115: \n116: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n117: - `CodeInterpreterHelper` struct exists with framework reference\n118: - `NewCodeInterpreterHelper(f *TestFramework) *CodeInterpreterHelper` constructor works\n119: - `CreateCodeInterpreter(ctx, ci) (*CodeInterpreter, error)` creates CodeInterpreter resource\n120: - `GetCodeInterpreter(ctx, name) (*CodeInterpreter, error)` retrieves CodeInterpreter by name\n121: - `WaitForCodeInterpreterReady(ctx, name, timeout) error` waits until CodeInterpreter is ready\n122: - `ExecuteCode(ctx, sessionID, code) (*ExecuteResponse, error)` executes code in session\n123: - `UploadFile(ctx, sessionID, filename, content) error` uploads file to session\n124: - `DownloadFile(ctx, sessionID, filename) ([]byte, error)` downloads file from session\n125: - All methods handle context cancellation properly\n126: - Unit tests verify each helper method\n127: \n128: **Dependencies:** T-1.3  \n129: **Estimated Time:** 3 hours\n130: \n131: ---\n132: \n133: ### 1.6 Implement Custom Assertions\n134: \n135: **Task ID:** T-1.6  \n136: **Description:** Implement custom Gomega matchers for common assertions\n137: \n138: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/assertions.go`\n139: \n140: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n141: - `EventuallyWithTimeout(actual, timeout, intervals) AsyncAssertion` wrapper exists\n142: - `ConsistentlyWithTimeout(actual, timeout, intervals) AsyncAssertion` wrapper exists\n143: - `HaveConditions(expected...) OmegaMatcher` verifies resource conditions\n144: - `BeReady() OmegaMatcher` verifies resource Ready status is true\n145: - `HavePhase(phase) OmegaMatcher` verifies resource phase matches\n146: - `HaveEndpoint(endpoint) OmegaMatcher` verifies service endpoint exists\n147: - `ReturnSuccess() OmegaMatcher` verifies HTTP 2xx response\n148: - `ReturnStatusCode(code) OmegaMatcher` verifies specific HTTP status code\n149: - `HaveSessionID() OmegaMatcher` verifies response contains session ID\n150: - All matchers have descriptive failure messages\n151: - Unit tests verify each matcher behavior\n152: \n153: **Dependencies:** T-1.2  \n154: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n155: \n156: ---\n157: \n158: ### 1.7 Create Test Fixtures\n159: \n160: **Task ID:** T-1.7  \n161: **Description:** Implement fixture generators for test resources\n162: \n163: **File:** `test/e2e/framework/fixtures.go`\n164: \n165: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n166: - `NewTestAgentRuntime(name) *AgentRuntime` creates AgentRuntime with minimal valid spec\n167: - `NewTestAgentRuntimeWithSpec(name, spec) *AgentRuntime` creates AgentRuntime with custom spec\n168: - `NewTestCodeInterpreter(name) *CodeInterpreter` creates CodeInterpreter with minimal valid spec\n169: - `NewTestCodeInterpreterWithSpec(name, spec) *CodeInterpreter` creates CodeInterpreter with custom spec\n170: - `NewTestSessionRequest(kind, name, namespace) *CreateSandboxRequest` creates session request\n171: - `NewTestInvokePayload(data map[string]interface{}) []byte` creates JSON payload\n172: - Fixtures use sensible defaults (e.g., nginx:latest for container image)\n173: - Fixtures include required fields for resource creation\n174: - Unit tests verify fixture generation\n175: \n176: **Dependencies:** T-1.4, T-1.5  \n177: **Estimated Time:** 1.5 hours\n178: \n179: ---\n180: \n181: ## Phase 2: AgentRuntime Tests\n182: \n183: ### 2.1 Implement AgentRuntime Test Suite\n184: \n185: **Task ID:** T-2.1  \n186: **Description:** Create main AgentRuntime E2E test suite with Ginkgo\n187: \n188: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/agentruntime_suite_test.go`\n189: \n190: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n191: - Test suite file exists with proper package declaration\n192: - `Describe(\"AgentRuntime E2E\", func() { ... })` top-level describe block\n193: - `BeforeSuite` initializes framework and waits for AgentCube to be ready\n194: - `AfterSuite` performs cleanup unless `SkipCleanup` is enabled\n195: - Framework and helper variables declared at suite level\n196: - Namespace variable declared at suite level\n197: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/` runs without errors\n198: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/ -ginkgo.v` shows suite structure\n199: \n200: **Dependencies:** T-1.7  \n201: **Estimated Time:** 1 hour\n202: \n203: ---\n204: \n205: ### 2.2 Implement AgentRuntime Creation Tests\n206: \n207: **Task ID:** T-2.2  \n208: **Description:** Implement tests for AgentRuntime creation workflows\n209: \n210: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/creation_test.go`\n211: \n212: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n213: - `Context(\"AgentRuntime Creation\", func() { ... })` context block\n214: - `It(\"should create AgentRuntime successfully\")` verifies creation succeeds\n215: - `It(\"should apply default values\")` verifies defaults (MaxSessionDuration: 8h, SessionTimeout: 15m)\n216: - `It(\"should become ready\")` verifies Ready status becomes true\n217: - Tests verify Name and Namespace are set correctly\n218: - Tests verify default values are applied\n219: - Tests verify status transitions to Ready\n220: - All tests have appropriate timeouts\n221: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/ -run AgentRuntimeCreation` passes with valid deployment\n222: \n223: **Dependencies:** T-2.1  \n224: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: ### 2.3 Implement AgentRuntime Invocation Tests\n229: \n230: **Task ID:** T-2.3  \n231: **Description:** Implement tests for AgentRuntime session invocation workflows\n232: \n233: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/invocation_test.go`\n234: \n235: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n236: - `Context(\"AgentRuntime Invocation\", func() { ... })` context block\n237: - `BeforeEach` creates AgentRuntime and waits for ready\n238: - `It(\"should create session successfully\")` verifies session creation returns session ID\n239: - `It(\"should invoke session successfully\")` verifies invocation returns 200 status\n240: - `It(\"should handle concurrent invocations\")` verifies 10 concurrent invocations all succeed\n241: - Tests verify session ID is non-empty\n242: - Tests verify invoke response contains expected data\n243: - Tests use goroutines and sync.WaitGroup for concurrency\n244: - Tests have appropriate timeouts\n245: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/ -run AgentRuntimeInvocation` passes with valid deployment\n246: \n247: **Dependencies:** T-2.2  \n248: **Estimated Time:** 2.5 hours\n249: \n250: ---\n251: \n252: ### 2.4 Implement AgentRuntime Lifecycle Tests\n253: \n254: **Task ID:** T-2.4  \n255: **Description:** Implement tests for AgentRuntime lifecycle management\n256: \n257: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/lifecycle_test.go`\n258: \n259: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n260: - `Context(\"AgentRuntime Lifecycle\", func() { ... })` context block\n261: - `It(\"should handle session expiration\")` verifies expired session cannot be invoked\n262: - `It(\"should delete session successfully\")` verifies deleted session cannot be invoked\n263: - Expiration test uses short timeout (30s) and waits 35s\n264: - Deletion test invokes session, deletes, then verifies deletion\n265: - Tests verify error is returned for expired/deleted sessions\n266: - Tests have appropriate timeouts\n267: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/ -run AgentRuntimeLifecycle` passes with valid deployment\n268: \n269: **Dependencies:** T-2.3  \n270: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n271: \n272: ---\n273: \n274: ### 2.5 Implement AgentRuntime Error Handling Tests\n275: \n276: **Task ID:** T-2.5  \n277: **Description:** Implement tests for AgentRuntime error scenarios\n278: \n279: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/error_handling_test.go`\n280: \n281: **Acceptance Criteria:**\n282: - `Context(\"AgentRuntime Error Handling\", func() { ... })` context block\n283: - `It(\"should reject invalid spec\")` verifies invalid spec returns error\n284: - `It(\"should reject non-existent session invocation\")` verifies error for missing session\n285: - `It(\"should handle malformed payload\")` verifies error handling for bad payload\n286: - `It(\"should handle timeout\")` verifies timeout error\n287: - Tests verify appropriate error messages\n288: - Tests verify error codes\n289: - Tests have appropriate timeouts\n290: - `go test ./test/e2e/agentruntime/ -run AgentRuntimeErrorHandling` passes with valid deployment\n291: \n292: **Dependencies:** T-2.4  \n293: **Estimated Time:** 2 hours\n294: \n295: ---\n296: \n297: ### 2.6 Implement AgentRuntime Concurrent Access Tests\n298: \n299: **Task ID:** T-2.6  \n300: **Description:** Implement tests for concurrent AgentRuntime operations\n301: \n302: **File:** `test/e2e/agentruntime/concurrent_test.go`\n303: \n304