xponentialBackoff utility\n\n7. **framework/failure_handler.go** (349 lines)\n   - TestFailureHandler for diagnostic collection\n   - Pod logs, resource status, and events collection\n   - Test metrics recording\n   - Diagnostic file management\n\n### Test Suites (3 files, 884 lines)\n1. **agentruntime/agentruntime_suite_test.go** (295 lines)\n   - 5 test contexts with 15+ test cases\n   - Creation, invocation, lifecycle, error handling, concurrent access tests\n\n2. **codeinterpreter/codeinterpreter_suite_test.go** (280 lines)\n   - 5 test contexts with 15+ test cases\n   - Creation, execution, file operations, error handling, concurrent access tests\n\n3. **integration/integration_suite_test.go** (309 lines)\n   - 6 test contexts with 10+ test cases\n   - Workflow, cross-resource, session management, scalability, cleanup, recovery tests\n\n### Test Manifests (4 files)\n1. **manifests/agentruntimes/simple-agent.yaml** - Minimal AgentRuntime\n2. **manifests/agentruntimes/multi-container-agent.yaml** - Multi-container AgentRuntime\n3. **manifests/codeinterpreters/python-interpreter.yaml** - Python interpreter\n4. **manifests/codeinterpreters/node-interpreter.yaml** - Node.js interpreter\n\n### Documentation (3 files)\n1. **README.md** - Comprehensive test suite documentation\n2. **RUNNING_TESTS.md** - Step-by-step test execution guide\n3. **design.md** - Technical design document (already existed)\n\n## Total Implementation Statistics\n\n- **Total Go Files**: 10 files (7 framework + 3 test suites)\n- **Total Lines of Code**: 3,660 lines\n- **Total YAML Files**: 4 test manifests\n- **Total Documentation**: 3 comprehensive MD files\n- **Test Cases**: 40+ individual test cases\n- **Test Contexts**: 16 test contexts\n- **Custom Matchers**: 10+ Gomega matchers\n- **Test Fixtures**: 20+ fixture generators\n\n## Key Features\n\n### Complete Test Framework\n- Kubernetes client initialization and management\n- Namespace lifecycle management\n- AgentCube readiness verification